1
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:50,520
Students,

2
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,920
we will have a self-study class next period.

3
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,120
Ask questions if you don't understand.

4
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,920
Class monitor, write down whoever makes trouble.

5
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,640
Class dismissed.

6
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,479
Stand up.

7
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:01,800
Goodbye, teacher.

8
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,130
Goodbye, students.

9
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:09,919
Dude,

10
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,520
could you explain this question to me?

11
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,850
I don't know how to do it.

12
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,640
Tell me. I really don't know.

13
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,640
Will this really work?

14
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,160
You'll see in a minute.

15
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,600
Explain this question to me too.

16
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,730
I don't know either.

17
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:28,579
Jingu, I don't quite know this question either.

18
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,660
Brother Jingu,

19
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,960
can you explain this question to me?

20
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,400
Jingu.

21
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:42,050
I don't know this question either.

22
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,450
I don't know this question either.

23
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:51,140
I think I have questions I don't know too.

24
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,079
Well,

25
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,300
you have questions to ask too?

26
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,920
Deskmate.

27
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,840
I know because of Xinrui,

28
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:08,170
you've always had a knot in your heart.

29
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,880
But it's in the past.

30
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,920
Mutou and I have let it go.

31
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,090
You should let it go too.

32
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,920
We're all classmates.

33
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,480
If you distance yourself from us on purpose,

34
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,040
we'll be very sad too.

35
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,320
I'm not distancing myself from you.

36
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,160
It's just that

37
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,730
I don't know how to face you.

38
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,079
We've been classmates for so many years.

39
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:31,160
Let's put those petty things aside.

40
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,800
We're still good brothers.

41
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,480
Exactly.

42
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,880
We are the five Zhicheng brothers.

43
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,880
We can't do without any of us, right?

44
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,010
It's break time.

45
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,220
Want to play a game?

46
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,040
Do you dare?

47
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,400
Come on, Alpha.

48
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,680
Great.

49
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,760
Okay.

50
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,280
Come on.

51
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,240
Come on.

52
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,360
Okay.

53
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,560
Time never speaks,

54
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,000
but it heals everything.

55
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,280
Sorry.

56
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,120
Qiao Yan.

57
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,780
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

58
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,400
Nothing.

59
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
I just had a fight with my mom

60
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,800
and she scolded me.

61
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,440
I get scolded a lot.

62
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,760
You'll get used to it.

63
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:51,940
Where are you going alone in the middle of the night?

64
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,880
I don't know.

65
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,720
You had a fight with your parents,

66
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,240
ran away from home, and don't know where to go.

67
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:56,800
Right?

68
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,200
I can tell you lack experience in this.

69
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,240
I have experience.

70
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,300
Come on, I'll take you to a good place.

71
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,600
Where?

72
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,920
You did very well.

73
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:09,720
Grandma,

74
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,120
how many times have you watched this?

75
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,280
You're still watching it.

76
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,520
It's a good show.

77
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,120
The acting is great.

78
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,640
Grandma,

79
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,200
I heard that tomorrow afternoon,

80
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,520
Shenghuo Supermarket is having a promotion.

81
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:25,360
They're giving away free eggs if you line up.

82
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,290
Do you want to go?

83
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,320
What time?

84
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,730
How many per person?

85
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,440
Tomorrow at 3:00 p.m.

86
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,250
I don't know how many we can get.

87
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,020
Grandma, where are you going?

88
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,200
Getting a bag to collect the eggs.

89
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,700
Here, have some water.

90
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,200
What happened to you?

91
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,840
Nothing.

92
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,860
I just bumped into something accidentally.

93
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:04,200
You're a girl but you have more injuries than a boy.

94
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,800
You're quite tough.

95
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,480
Shang Ningyu,

96
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,570
have you ever thought about running away?

97
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,520
Running away?

98
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,000
Where to?

99
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,480
Like,

100
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,840
to a place where no one knows you,

101
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,120
and start a new life.

102
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:24,600
That won't work. I can't stay idle.

103
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,720
If I don't have family

104
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,120
or friends to talk to,

105
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,680
I'll go crazy.

106
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,360
I think I'm sick.

107
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:36,400
Sick? What's wrong?

108
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,000
Have you seen a doctor?

109
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,120
What are your symptoms?

110
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,720
Well,

111
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:46,760
I've been feeling depressed all the time

112
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,360
and staying awake all night.

113
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:54,460
Not being able to sleep isn't an illness.

114
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,320
You just have too much pressure from studying.

115
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,560
Working so hard, no wonder you can't sleep well.

116
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,240
By the way,

117
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,280
in a few days, Mr. Men

118
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:02,010
is taking everyone out, right?

119
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,800
To go camping.

120
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,060
You should come along.

121
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,120
Camping?

122
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,120
Where to?

123
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,300
Ronghua Mountain.

124
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,560
I heard there'll be a meteor shower that night.

125
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,960
Going to see the meteor shower with you

126
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,320
as it falls on this earth.

127
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,000
Go mountain climbing.

128
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,720
Where is it?

129
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,820
It's fine. Come in.

130
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,600
Um, hello.

131
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,800
Where can I get the free eggs?

132
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:41,610
All the way inside, turn right.

133
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,600
Thank you. Thank you.

134
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,570
You're welcome.

135
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:55,760
What are you doing?

136
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,120
I... I'm not buying this.

137
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,760
Grandma.

138
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:59,440
You're the lucky winner of our event.

139
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:01,360
You need to collect the eggs with a sense of ceremony.

140
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,520
This scarf is for you.

141
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,400
For me?

142
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,800
It's pretty nice.

143
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,320
All right. Thank you.

144
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,060
Where are the eggs?

145
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,720
This way.

146
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,559
Look here, Grandma.

147
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,800
We are already at this age.

148
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,360
How much more good time do we have left to waste?

149
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:02,360
Wenying.

150
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,090
Every day in the future,

151
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,690
are you willing to let me spend it with you?

152
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,880
Romantic,

153
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:09,360
warm,

154
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,080
and loving.

155
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,160
Grandpa, Grandma, I know

156
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,240
that in your era,

157
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,800
expressing feelings was implicit

158
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,060
and you might feel shy.

159
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,880
So we took the liberty

160
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,800
of planning this surprise for you.

161
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,800
I hope you like it.

162
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,160
We also sincerely hope

163
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,320
that in the days to come,

164
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,540
the life you live can be romantic,

165
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,240
warm,

166
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,400
and full of love.

167
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,680
Well, um,

168
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:40,320
I should go back and ask my granddaughter

169
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,680
and family first.

170
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,480
Grandma!

171
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,160
Grandma!

172
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,640
I support you!

173
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,200
Grandma, I support you too!

174
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:07,840
Grandma, we all support you.

175
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,080
Grandma.

176
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:12,920
For over ten years,

177
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:16,080
you have raised me with complete devotion.

178
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,320
I really don't know

179
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,040
how to repay you.

180
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,600
I'm about to go to college

181
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,770
and we'll go our separate ways.

182
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,000
If there's no one to love

183
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,480
and take care of you,

184
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,720
how can I be at ease?

185
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:34,680
Thank you, child. I will listen to you.

186
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:38,600
I still want to help raise your children.

187
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,080
Wenying.

188
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,440
I'm here.

189
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,800
Let me stay with you

190
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,760
and take care of our grandchildren.

191
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,560
Okay?

192
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:17,080
Grandma, it's been so many years.

193
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:20,240
I finally see you smiling so happily again.

194
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,560
That's great.

195
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:25,360
From now on, you two are real brothers.

196
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,200
I'm even your older brother now.

197
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,480
Did you hit a girl or not?

198
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,400
You don't even believe your brother.

199
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,720
We've known each other for so long.

200
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,850
Don't you know what kind of person I am?

201
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,600
True.

202
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:42,840
In that case,

203
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,580
I have two older brothers.

204
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,890
Let's see who dares to bully me now.

205
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:52,280
So who is older?

206
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:55,320
Who is the older brother and who is the younger?

207
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,240
Of course I'm the older brother.

208
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,640
He is my younger brother.

209
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:01,360
Come on, call me brother.

210
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,240
Bro, bro, bro.

211
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,120
Good boy.

212
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,000
But the way you call me

213
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,740
sounds like a hen laying eggs.

214
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:16,880
Who are you calling a mother hen laying eggs?

215
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,080
Stop messing around.

216
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:21,920
Gong Yu,

217
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:24,640
I used to be rude to you.

218
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,340
Don't take it to heart.

219
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,740
It's fine. That's in the past.

220
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,880
Do you think I'm that fragile?

221
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:35,040
But when I join the army,

222
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,760
I hope you can help

223
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,800
take care of my grandpa.

224
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,540
You are my brother,

225
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,400
and Mutou is your younger brother.

226
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,360
With us around,

227
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:45,440
you can safely leave Grandpa Gong to us.

228
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,240
Right, Mutou?

229
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:46,920
Yes.

230
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,840
We will take good care of him.

231
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,720
Thanks.

232
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,400
As for Ruirui,

233
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,120
do you want to talk to her?

234
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,640
I know what you mean.

235
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,240
On the day of the New Year's Eve camping,

236
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,970
I will have a good talk with her.

237
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,560
Yuanbao,

238
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:16,490
when is Grandpa Gong moving to your house?

239
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,080
Not yet.

240
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:20,480
He said he'll move after New Year's Day.

241
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:21,760
Then will Gong Yu

242
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,840
stay at your house during holidays?

243
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:25,800
I don't think so.

244
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:27,200
There's no place to stay.

245
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:28,920
That makes sense.

246
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,560
Shang Ningyu, what are you looking at?

247
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,280
N-Nothing.

248
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:55,370
Give it to me.

249
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:02,200
You can't even remember Newton's laws.

250
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,360
You still have time to read this?

251
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,440
With your level,

252
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:07,290
can you even understand a military magazine?

253
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,960
Class,

254
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:15,120
the day after tomorrow is the last day of 2007.

255
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,720
The day after that is New Year's Day.

256
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,160
Those of you going camping

257
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,200
must wear more clothes.

258
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,280
The class monitor will

259
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:22,200
distribute the guidelines to everyone.

260
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,330
Have fun, everyone.

261
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,360
Wait for me. I can't carry this anymore.

262
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:45,090
Yuanbao, let's go to that room.

263
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:46,280
I can't carry this anymore.

264
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,960
Awesome.

265
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:52,800
Class.

266
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,760
Without delaying your studies,

267
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:56,920
to cheer you up,

268
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,260
I'm taking you to see a meteor shower.

269
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:01,320
Today,

270
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,440
you don't have to treat me as your teacher.

271
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,080
I won't teach you anything about studying either.

272
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,280
Just have fun.

273
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,840
Wait, note two things.

274
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:11,720
First,

275
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,040
no littering.

276
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,560
Second, be safe.

277
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,280
Go play.

278
00:16:20,560 --> 00:16:22,760
This is pretty. Take it for decoration.

279
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,160
My grandpa asked me

280
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:26,200
to bring you guys lots of good food.

281
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,280
I'll share it with you later.

282
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:28,080
Really?

283
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,800
If Yuanbao hears this,

284
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,250
she'll be thrilled.

285
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,000
Thank Grandpa for us.

286
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:38,120
That secret you whispered in my ear,

287
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,200
does she know it?

288
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,000
I said it's a secret.

289
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,860
You can't let her know.

290
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:46,860
Don't betray me now that you're her brother.

291
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:50,130
You're the top guy of Zhicheng,

292
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,600
and you're still afraid?

293
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,160
Hurry up, Yuanbao.

294
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,760
Hurry up and tidy up these snacks.

295
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,440
Hurry.

296
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,480
You guys outside, hurry up.

297
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,079
Bring the snacks in.

298
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,200
You're the only one talking.

299
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,000
Where should I put this?

300
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,640
I'm just urging you on.

301
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:08,960
Class rep, let me help you.

302
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,480
No, thanks.

303
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,720
Now you know why you're fat.

304
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,720
Put this over there.

305
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,599
Put this here.

306
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,000
This is mine.

307
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,240
Bring it here.

308
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,400
Yuanbao.

309
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,200
What is it?

310
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,619
Matching couple outfits!

311
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,840
Not bad, Meng Jingu.

312
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:30,760
When did this happen?

313
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,560
I really didn't see this coming.

314
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:34,060
What a pleasant surprise!

315
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:39,040
Put your clothes on properly, don't catch a cold.

316
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:39,800
Be careful.

317
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,420
Put this on, don't freeze.

318
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:49,780
Come on, let's tidy up.

319
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,400
I'm late.

320
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,560
Qiao Yan.

321
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:57,520
Your clothes look so good.

322
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,120
Your clothes look great.

323
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,200
Where did you buy them?

324
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,360
Can you tell me?

325
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,640
Why did you buy so many things?

326
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,920
Here, give them to me.

327
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:06,560
I bought some snacks for everyone.

328
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,160
We already bought a lot.

329
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,760
Don't let them go to waste.

330
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:14,680
I'm usually not very nice with my words.

331
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,760
I might have unintentionally hurt everyone's feelings.

332
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,440
I wanted to buy more snacks

333
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:20,440
as an apology.

334
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:21,840
What are you talking about?

335
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:22,920
We are all friends.

336
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,200
No need to be so polite.

337
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,880
Come on, let's tidy up together.

338
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:27,080
I heard on the news

339
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:29,320
that the meteor shower isn't until eleven.

340
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,720
Come on.

341
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,280
Ruirui.

342
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:37,560
I hid a can of delicious snacks for you.

343
00:18:37,560 --> 00:18:38,890
What delicious snacks?

344
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:43,720
Potato chips.

345
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:45,250
Aren't they your favorite?

346
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:02,050
Grandpa asked me to bring you two some snacks.

347
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:03,520
Thank you, Grandpa.

348
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,160
Not thanking me?

349
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:10,490
Thank you, brother.

350
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:12,280
Good girl, eat up.

351
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:16,410
Let's eat together.

352
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,600
Jingu.

353
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:27,080
What are you listening to?

354
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,080
Let me listen too.

355
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:44,040
Well, I like listening to music too.

356
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:44,800
Make some room.

357
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,800
Let me listen too.

358
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:47,610
What song are you listening to?

359
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:51,440
Nice earphones.

360
00:19:55,480 --> 00:19:56,280
A love song?

361
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,160
It just shuffled to this one.

362
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:18,500
You're going to join the army?

363
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,200
That's great.

364
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,780
Yes, I'm joining the army.

365
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:37,280
You're leaving?

366
00:20:38,760 --> 00:20:40,020
I'm leaving next week.

367
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:51,680
Come on, let's talk.

368
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,760
Well, you guys talk first.

369
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:00,300
I'm going to the restroom.

370
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,560
During this time,

371
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,600
I've been deeply moved.

372
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,080
Seeing

373
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:15,040
how sincerely you do things for each other,

374
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:17,200
I feel really satisfied.

375
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,920
To be a part of your group,

376
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:20,620
I'm very happy.

377
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:26,640
But just as I realized how great everyone is,

378
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,560
I have to leave.

379
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:30,850
Why do you want to join the army?

380
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:33,400
I've always wanted to win glory for my country,

381
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,320
so I can be like my father

382
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,450
and become a soldier

383
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:36,980
to defend the country.

384
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,160
I heard

385
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:42,890
that your father

386
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,000
passed away.

387
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:50,420
He sacrificed himself to save a drowning child.

388
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,200
But in my heart,

389
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:55,010
he has always been a hero

390
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:58,200
and the role model I want to be for my whole life.

391
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,920
I also hope your dream comes true

392
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:01,720
and you become an angel in white.

393
00:22:03,840 --> 00:22:04,840
I'll work hard.

394
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,600
Actually,

395
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,260
what I really want to say today is that

396
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,260
whether it's friendship,

397
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:13,330
family love,

398
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:16,440
or those feelings we don't quite understand yet,

399
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:19,010
they are all very precious affections

400
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:23,720
and wonderful connections between people.

401
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:27,320
We can cherish this friendship between us.

402
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:29,280
And you

403
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:32,520
shouldn't ignore other people's feelings anymore.

404
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:34,880
O-Other people?

405
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:40,280
Like the person hiding behind the tree behind you.

406
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:51,440
In fact, between people,

407
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:54,050
there are not that many insurmountable gaps.

408
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,960
Sometimes, a reminder

409
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,280
or a joke

410
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:59,400
is enough to eliminate the estrangement between us,

411
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,840
so we can open our hearts to each other

412
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:02,300
and become close friends.

413
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:05,080
Perhaps this is the charm of youth,

414
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,880
simple and pure.

415
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:14,440
Is Gong Yu really going to join the army?

416
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:18,040
Yes, he's leaving in a few days.

417
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:22,000
Fortunately, he doesn't have to worry about his grandfather anymore.

418
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,840
Actually, he's a really nice guy,

419
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:25,680
just not good at expressing himself.

420
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,280
When others misunderstand him,

421
00:23:27,280 --> 00:23:28,880
he doesn't explain too much.

422
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:33,280
The things I did to him before,

423
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:35,400
I hope he really doesn't mind.

424
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:36,600
All right.

425
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,000
Gong Yu is not a petty person.

426
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,780
This is also a good lesson for you.

427
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:43,680
You can't be so arbitrary in the future,

428
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,480
got it?

429
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,480
Got it.

430
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:49,360
In a few years,

431
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:51,290
when we go to school out of town,

432
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,970
Grandma will at least have someone to talk to.

433
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:56,200
You don't need to worry too much.

434
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:59,280
I think it's pretty good too.

435
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:10,000
Look, everyone! The meteor shower is here.

436
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,440
Look over there!

437
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,000
Hurry!

438
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,200
Come here!

439
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:22,720
Make a wish!

440
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:26,800
I hope Grandma, Grandpa, Uncle, Aunt,

441
00:24:27,040 --> 00:24:28,000
and Mutou,

442
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:30,200
will all be safe and healthy,

443
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:32,360
and stay happily together forever.

444
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:33,640
Also,

445
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,120
I hope Mutou and I

446
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:37,180
can get into an ideal university,

447
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:40,320
and have a bright and beautiful future.

448
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:44,680
I hope Yuanbao's wishes all come true.

449
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:47,720
I hope I can get into

450
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,640
the Physics Department of Qingbei University as I wish.

451
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:52,800
I also hope my friends' dreams come true.

452
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:56,640
I hope my children stay safe and healthy

453
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:58,760
and get into their ideal universities.

454
00:24:58,760 --> 00:24:59,560
Also,

455
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:03,000
when will I stop being single?

456
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:05,200
I hope my dad will agree

457
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:07,040
to let me buy those new sneakers.

458
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:08,560
I hope next year

459
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,800
my cultivation level will improve,

460
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,240
and I can understand Qimen Dunjia.

461
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:15,210
Tuibeitu would be fine too.

462
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:16,810
The I Ching is also okay.

463
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:25,080
May all the wishes of the people I love come true.

464
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:28,760
I hope I can be happy every day,

465
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:31,440
and always have a bright smile.

466
00:25:32,360 --> 00:25:35,040
I hope everyone who likes me,

467
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:37,200
and everyone I like,

468
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:40,680
can be safe, happy, and achieve their dreams.

469
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,360
I hope Tong Ruirui

470
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,360
will notice me one day.

471
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:49,400
I hope I can be happy in my next life.

472
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:53,440
Nine.

473
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,320
Seven.

474
00:25:55,560 --> 00:25:56,120
Six.

475
00:26:01,040 --> 00:26:03,760
Happy New Year!

476
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:08,760
2008, here we come!

477
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:14,920
2008, wishing my classmates a bright future.

478
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:19,280
2008, I hope we can always be together.

479
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:23,040
2008, let me have more PE classes.

480
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:26,080
2008, make it to the top eight.

481
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:29,280
2008, I want a holiday every day.

482
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:37,520
2008, keep going.

483
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:41,690
I hope everyone around me gets better and better.

484
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:44,920
2008, victory in the Olympics!

485
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:48,480
2008, I hope I can grow a bit taller.

486
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:51,880
2008, I hope you stay healthy.

487
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:56,640
I hope everyone's wishes come true.

488
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,330
That silly girl Tong Ruirui

489
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,130
is sleeping so soundly.

490
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:12,500
I can't wake her up.

491
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:16,000
In the middle of nowhere,

492
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:19,000
I dared to go to the bathroom alone.

493
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:22,120
I can brag about this to Mutou for a year.

494
00:27:23,040 --> 00:27:23,880
It's so cold.

495
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,120
Qiao Yan.

496
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:33,700
Are you going to the bathroom?

497
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:35,800
It's so dark. I'll go with you.

498
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,640
It's not safe for you to go alone.

499
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,640
No need, Yuanbao.

500
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,040
I can go by myself.

501
00:27:40,080 --> 00:27:40,800
Thank you.

502
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,960
It's fine. I just came back from there.

503
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,820
The road is really hard to walk on.

504
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:45,720
Besides,

505
00:27:45,800 --> 00:27:47,800
we can keep each other company.

506
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,530
It's fine. I'll go with you.

507
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:50,680
I'm not sleepy anyway.

508
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:52,340
I have nothing to be afraid of.

509
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:56,040
Yuanbao, I just can't sleep.

510
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:57,610
I want to get some fresh air.

511
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,180
I'll just walk around here

512
00:27:59,280 --> 00:28:00,540
and won't go anywhere.

513
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,160
Don't worry about me.

514
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:03,280
Qiao Yan,

515
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,600
you don't look well.

516
00:28:06,320 --> 00:28:07,440
Are you okay?

517
00:28:08,840 --> 00:28:09,560
I'm fine.

518
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:11,920
I really just can't sleep.

519
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:13,960
Go back and rest.

520
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:14,840
Go to sleep.

521
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,080
Don't worry about me.

522
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,440
Okay.

523
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,520
Then be careful.

524
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,000
It's cold in the mountains at night.

525
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,160
You're wearing so little.

526
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,560
What if you catch a cold?

527
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,000
Right,

528
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:27,960
remember to take your phone.

529
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:30,120
Call me if anything happens.

530
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,120
Got it?

531
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:35,800
Yuanbao.

532
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:37,960
I used to

533
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,600
badmouth you a lot

534
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:42,600
and picked on you.

535
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,440
I'm sorry.

536
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:47,320
That's in the past.

537
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,080
Why bring it up now?

538
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:51,800
I just

539
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:54,480
feel a little guilty.

540
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:55,720
It's fine.

541
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:58,240
You know I don't hold grudges.

542
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,480
Besides,

543
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:01,240
I know you too well.

544
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:03,960
You may have a sharp tongue,

545
00:29:04,240 --> 00:29:05,920
but if I'm bullied,

546
00:29:06,320 --> 00:29:07,000
every time

547
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:09,450
you're always the first to stand up for me.

548
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:11,520
Yuanbao,

549
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:19,160
being your classmate and friend

550
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:21,410
makes me very happy.

551
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:25,480
Why are you suddenly being so cheesy?

552
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,360
It's nothing.

553
00:29:29,360 --> 00:29:32,080
I'm just being a little sentimental.

554
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,960
What's there to be sentimental about?

555
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:36,560
Winter break is coming soon.

556
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:37,720
During the New Year,

557
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:38,840
I'll call Shang Ningyu and Tong Ruirui,

558
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:39,840
and we'll all go out.

559
00:29:39,840 --> 00:29:41,040
We can hang out for a day,

560
00:29:41,040 --> 00:29:43,040
and all our worries will disappear.

561
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:46,480
Alright, I'm going back to sleep.

562
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:48,080
Rest early.

563
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,500
Don't go too far, okay?

564
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:53,840
Okay, I'm going back.

565
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:56,560
Yuanbao.

566
00:29:58,960 --> 00:29:59,820
Happy New Year.

567
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:01,680
Happy New Year.

568
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:53,640
Zaozao.

569
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,240
That little lazy pig is not awake yet.

570
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:56,920
Yuanbao.

571
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,560
She was gone before I got up.

572
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:00,560
I guess she went to the bathroom.

573
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,330
Morning, everyone.

574
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:06,900
The morning air on the mountain is really fresh.

575
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,440
What's wrong?

576
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:14,920
She's not answering.

577
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,520
Ruirui,

578
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:16,680
why don't you

579
00:31:16,760 --> 00:31:18,920
go to the restroom to look for her?

580
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,360
I'm a little worried.

581
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:22,120
Okay, I'll go take a look.

582
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:28,840
She's an adult. What's there to worry about?

583
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,160
There's nothing to worry about.

584
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:31,560
Qiao Yan is also not here.

585
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,720
Could they have left together?

586
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:35,010
Qiao Yan is not here.

587
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,680
Well, brother,

588
00:31:37,760 --> 00:31:39,840
why don't you give Qiao Yan a call?

589
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:40,720
I'll call.

590
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,520
Could it be that they were carried away

591
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:44,450
by a bear in the middle of the night?

592
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:55,040
She is not in the bathroom.

593
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:08,080
She didn't bring her phone.

594
00:32:08,080 --> 00:32:09,880
And she left two letters behind.

595
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:12,800
Could she have...

596
00:32:15,480 --> 00:32:17,840
Yaqi, go to the park administration for help.

597
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:19,600
Tong Ruirui, go find Mr. Tian.

598
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,570
Notify the school and her parents.

599
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:23,280
Shang Ningyu.

600
00:32:23,280 --> 00:32:24,400
Wake everyone up.

601
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,400
We'll split into four groups now.

602
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,600
Hurry up and find her.

603
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:27,400
Okay, okay.

604
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:30,040
Nightfall.

605
00:32:31,280 --> 00:32:32,160
Starlight.

606
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:34,120
City.

607
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:36,000
Fireworks.

608
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,370
Neon lights.

609
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:42,250
There are so many beautiful things in this world,

610
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,000
but none of them belong to me.

611
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,800
God is so unfair.

612
00:32:48,760 --> 00:32:50,020
How dare you talk back!

613
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,040
Talking back? I'll teach you to talk back!

614
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:52,720
Take that!
